()1️⃣ Govern ka Simple Matlab:-
Govern = control + monitor + manage access
Matlab ye ensure karna ki har user ke paas sirf wahi access ho jo unke kaam ke liye zaroori hai, aur koi unauthorized access na ho.
Ye basically Identity Governance ka main purpose hai.
Example:-
Rahul Finance team me hai → Sirf finance apps ka access chahiye
Agar usko IT admin app ka access mil gaya → Governance ke rules ke through detect aur fix hoga.

️⃣ SailPoint me Governance Components:-
Identity Governance – user ke access ka monitoring aur management
Policies – define karte hain ki kaun kya access le sakta hai
Access Reviews / Certification – managers / auditors regularly check karte hain ki users ka access sahi hai ya nahi
Roles / Entitlements – roles ke through access simplify kiya jata hai
Violations & Remediation – agar koi rule violate hota hai, automatically fix ya alert hota hai

9️⃣ Policy
Policy policy:-
Kya hai: Ye rules ka set hai jo access aur entitlements ko govern karta hai.
Kya karta hai:-
Access reviews, SoD, Least Privilege enforce karta hai
Violations detect karta hai,

()1️⃣ Remediation ka Simple Matlab:-
Remediation = koi problem / violation ko fix karna
Identity Governance me iska matlab hai: jab koi user ka access policy ya rule violate karta hai,
toh system automatically ya manually usko correct kare.
Example:-
Policy: Finance team ke alawa koi write access nahi le sakta.
Rahul galti se write access le leta hai.
Remediation → SailPoint automatically uska write access remove kar dega.

2️⃣ Remediation Types:-
()Automatic Remediation:-
SailPoint automatically entitlement remove, account disable, role revoke kar deta hai.
Example: context.removeLinkEntitlement(user, entitlement)

()Manual Remediation:-
Admin / manager ko alert milta hai aur woh manually action leta hai.
Example: Manager approve/revoke access via SailPoint dashboard.

()🔟 PolicyViolation:-
PolicyViolation violation
Kya hai: Ye ek incident hai jab policy breach hota hai (user ke paas extra access ya conflict roles).
Kya karta hai:-
Violation create karke alert aur remediation trigger karta hai.
